# 🍔 Food Courier UI (Qt/QML)

A modern and responsive Food Courier mobile application UI developed using Qt 6 and QML. This project recreates a food delivery app interface with onboarding screens, account creation, and login functionality.



## 📱 Features

- Onboarding Screen
- SwipeView Navigation
- Create Account Screen
- Login Screen
- TabBar Navigation
- Dynamic Tab Highlighting
- Google Authentication Button UI
- Responsive Layout
- Modern Material-inspired Design


## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Qt 6
- QML
- Qt Quick
- Qt Quick Controls Basic
- Qt Quick Layouts
- CMake



